OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FJust as Leicester City are teetering
OL,7,Fon the edge of relegation to League
OL,8,FOne, the club has announced losses of
OL,9,F#71 million in its annual accounts.
OL,11,FIt's obviously a disastrous place to
OL,12,Fbe for a club that won the Premier
OL,13,FLeague ten years ago, but just how bad
OL,14,Fis the financial side?
OL,16,FThe headline figure looks alarming,
OL,17,Fbut it's not unprecedented. Leicester
OL,18,FCity lost almost #90 million two years
OL,19,Fago and many football clubs have an
OL,20,Funhealthy dependence on owners
OL,21,Fplugging the gaps.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
