PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FIn 2023/24, Leicester City's losses
OL,7,Fwere down to #27 million, but the
OL,8,F'underlying operating position' is
OL,9,Factually better than it was then,
OL,10,Fmeaning income rose more than the
OL,11,Fcosts in returning to the Premier
OL,12,FLeague for 2024/25.
OL,14,FSo why is the loss so much bigger?
OL,16,FIn part, it's due to Leicester City
OL,17,Fselling Kiernan Dewsbury-Hall to
OL,18,FChelsea for #30 million in June 2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FThis helped to drive down losses in
OL,7,Fthe previous year's accounts, but
OL,8,Fhasn't helped these figures.
OL,10,FTo balance the books, the club relies
OL,11,Fon three sources of income:
OL,13,FThere is one big sign the club is
OL,14,Fmoving towards being more self
OL,15,Fsufficient.
OL,17,FPreviously wages were unsustainable
OL,18,Fand consistently running at over 100%
OL,19,Fof income, but this has reduced to 82%.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FStill too high for the financial minds
OL,7,Fat the club, but heading in the right
OL,8,Fdirection.
OL,10,FRelegation clauses in contracts should
OL,11,Fmean this doesn't rocket back up off
OL,12,Fthe back of falling into the
OL,13,FChampionship.
OL,15,FThere are further relegation clauses
OL,16,Fin place should they drop even lower.
OL,18,FNo one is working harder at Leicester
OL,19,FCity to sort this than the new chief
OL,20,Fexecutive Kevin Davies.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FThe club still hasn't filled his old
OL,7,Ffinancial director role, so he's been
OL,8,Fbusy to say the least.
OL,10,FHe is a Leicester man and was promoted
OL,11,Fbecause of his work in steering the
OL,12,Fclub's finances back towards something
OL,13,Fnear sanity.
OL,15,FHis task now is to plan for four
OL,16,Fdifferent sets of financial
OL,17,Fregulations, as both the Championship
OL,18,Fand League One decide whether to
OL,19,Fchange their respective rules.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FLeicester City were deducted six
OL,7,Fpoints this season for breaching
OL,8,FPremier League profit and
OL,9,Fsustainability rules, but their work
OL,10,Foff the pitch means they are much more
OL,11,Fconfident of sticking within the
OL,12,Flimits.
OL,14,FThis is not without pain.
OL,16,FDropping out of the Premier League
OL,17,Fmeans they have to pay back a high
OL,18,Finterest #50 million pound loan to
OL,19,FMacquarie Bank over two years. This is
OL,20,Feating into parachute payments, which
OL,21,Fwill run out next year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FShould the club be in League One,
OL,7,Fserious spending decisions will need
OL,8,Fto be made as the club will bring in
OL,9,Fless money.
OL,11,FEven with those spending cuts,
OL,12,FLeicester City would be by far and
OL,13,Faway the biggest spenders in League
OL,14,FOne and would expect an immediate
OL,15,Freturn to the Championship.
OL,17,FThe big fear is getting stuck or the
OL,18,Fownership suddenly losing interest -
OL,19,Fthere is no sign of the latter.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FWhilst many fans call for a change of
OL,7,Fowners, these accounts show the
OL,8,Fcontinued dependence on King Power and
OL,9,Fchairman Khun Top.
OL,11,FCollectively they've put in hundreds
OL,12,Fof millions of pounds over the years.
OL,14,FReports of financial problems for King
OL,15,FPower understandably worry supporters.
OL,17,FIt's difficult to know how bad that
OL,18,Fsituation is, but it's thought the
OL,19,Fclub's new chief executive would've
OL,20,Frejected the job if he had serious
OL,21,Fconcerns.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1774807894
OL,3,CLeicester City lost #71m and why it's
OL,4,Cnot the full picture
OL,6,FHe has levers to pull too, there is an
OL,7,Funused legal route to force King Power
OL,8,Finto giving the club money should that
OL,9,Fneed ever arise.
OL,11,FThe club got into a mess by
OL,12,Foverspending and failing to plan for
OL,13,Fworst-case scenarios.
OL,15,FIt appears those lessons have perhaps
OL,16,Fbeen learnt, which is timely as League
OL,17,FOne is staring them in the face.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
